snippet.title: Official Alpha Reveal Trailer | Steel Swarm: Apocalypse
snippet.description:
After six years of development, Clay Token Game Studio Inc is proud to deliver the next generation of MOBAs. Fight alongside swarms of minions in a fully destructible city. Fast-paced, action-packed, epic battles await. 

Sign up to play open alpha at https://steelswarm.net
